animeTitle: I Can See The Success Rate S2
synopsis: With the help of nobles, Bai Wu took the key step of destroying the counterfeiting group: joining the Antique Association and becoming a core member. The various difficulties encountered on the road to membership made Bai Wu even more convinced that there are insiders of a fraudulent group. Bai Wu's life, with the renewal of the success rate system, restarted again...
